{"type": "article", "id": 28412, "title": "3D 打印钢笔", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-20T06:55:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702151720Jw78RuW1I2d9zQLy.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>习惯了电子产品再拿起钢笔写字或许还会有一种不习惯的感觉，一支让人握起来更舒服的笔就成了解决问题的关键。<a href=\"http://www.giovannipagnotta.com/\">Pagnotta Design</a> 最近采用 3D 打印技术设计了一款钛合金钢笔 P22，符合人体工程学的设计带来的是流畅的造型以及恰到好处的平衡性，握笔时感觉好像会融化在指间一样。P22 通过旋转尾部控制笔芯进出，内置的墨水最长可以使用一年，之后可以在网上下订单进行补充。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/969974524/the-p22-pen\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 170 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151717WihspSbLay6M09Ix.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070215171889ZVpEnzxyD0oNQB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151718rwzCiLY0NvG9udZI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021517198F5jEYHdPrSKQAu7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}